```

## What's included

| Layer | Detail |
|---|---|
| Model | `IntegrationItems` (externalId, status, payload, processedAt, errorMessage) + `StagingItems` |
| Service | `IntegrationService` â€” OData v4, `@requires: 'authenticated-user'`, `@restrict` per role |
| Handler | `process` action, `before(CREATE)` default status, structured logging via `@argos/cap-lib` |
| Tests | Happy-path integration test + mock-external helper |
| Auth | Mocked users in `.cdsrc.json` (roles: `admin`, `processor`, `viewer`) |
| HTTP hardening | `@argos/cap-ops` wired in bootstrap: HSTS, CSP, X-Frame-Options, Referrer-Policy |
